<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182875>
    bibo:endPage "68" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "58" ;
    bibo:volume "1814" ;
    dc:creator "Rödder, Dennis; Jungfer, Karl-Heinz" ;
    dc:date "2008" ;
    dc:title "A new Pristimantis (Anura, Strabomantidae) from Yuruaní-tepui, Venezuela" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182876>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182877>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182878>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182879>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182880>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182881> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182876>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Female holotype (ZFMK 87278) of Pristimantis yuruaniensis sp. nov. in dorsal (A), ventral (B), and lateral view (C). Scale: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182876/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182877>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Female holotype of Pristimantis yuruaniensis sp. nov. Note enlarged conical tubercle on upper eye lid (A) and fine middorsal raphe (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182877/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182878>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Further specimens of Pristimantis yuruaniensis sp. nov. and its type locality. A-C: specimens not collected from Yuruaní-tepui. D: female Pristimantis yuruanienis sp. nov. with egg clutch in terrarium. This frog belongs to the type series, but there are no records as to which of them it is. E: type locality of Pristimantis yuruaniensis sp. nov. on top of Yuruaní-tepui. F: Pristimantis cf. yuruanienis, uncollected specimen photographed on Kukenán-tepui. Photos: H. Mägdefrau." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182878/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182879>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Hand (A), foot (B), and head of the preserved holotype of Pristimantis yuruaniensis sp. nov. in dorsal (C) and lateral (D) view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182879/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182880>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Oscillogram and sonagram of the advertisement call of Pristimantis yuruanienis sp. nov. (specimen not collected)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182880/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182881>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Map of the Guayana region with the location of the Yuruani and Kukenán-tepui." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182881/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

